OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 06 APR
OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1968FThe 13th Eurovision Song Contest
OL,7,Fairs on BBC One.
OL,8,
OL,9,FIt is held at the Royal Albert Hall in
OL,10,FLondon. Spain wins the contest with the
OL,11,Fsong La, La, La, performed by Massiel.
OL,12,
OL,13,FThe event was broadcast in colour for
OL,14,Fthe first time. However, because BBC
OL,15,FOne did not yet broadcast in colour,
OL,16,FBBC Two aired a repeat of the show, in
OL,17,Fcolour, the following day.
