OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1974FThe 19th Eurovision Song Contest
OL,7,Fairs on BBC One, live from The Dome,
OL,8,FBrighton. Katie Boyle presented, with
OL,9,FDavid Vine providing the commentary.
OL,10,FOlivia Newton-John was joint-4th for
OL,11,Fthe UK and Sweden's Abba famously won
OL,12,Fwith Waterloo.
OL,13,
OL,14,CG1985FThe first edition of The Max
OL,15,FHeadroom Show airs on Channel 4.
OL,16,
OL,17,CG1988FThe final episode of A Very
OL,18,FPeculiar Practice airs on BBC Two.
OL,19,
OL,20,CG1989FThe first edition of Rolf's
OL,21,FCartoon Club airs on ITV.
OL,22,
